
The Season of Men  ni filime y'ikinamico yo mu 2000 y’Abafaransa-Tuniziya iyobowe na Moufida Tlatli . Yerekanwe mu gice cya Un Certain Regard mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2000 .  Umutwe wa filime, Igihe cy'abagabo, werekeza ukwezi kumwe kwumwaka abagabo  baza ku kirwa cya Djerba. 

